Food is really good but unfortunately the  waitress was extremely rude. She slammed our food on the table and when we inquired about her attitude she walked away and began to speak in her Native language.   She treated everyone else with respect except for us who only spoke English and not French. I've traveled to many countries interacting with many cultures and have never experienced Racism first hand from someone who's skin was full of Melanin as mines. It goes to show how far we as a people still have to go.  So disappointed in her and her action.  Would not recommend this establishment if you're not fluent in French you will be treated as less than.
